verbose_text: The results showed that DEX exposure for 28 days significantly increased the expression of NLRP-1 and ASC (XREF_FIG, P < 0.05 and P < 0.01), caspase-1 and caspase-5 (XREF_FIG, P < 0.05 and P < 0.01) and IL-1beta and IL-18 (XREF_FIG, P < 0.01).
